    "1651266332e8454b0d": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "1651266332e6feb2da-0": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Flowing Against The Stream",
            "use_h1": false
          }
        },
        "1651266332e6feb2da-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>When it comes to packaging, we only use what is necessary while minimizing waste. <\/p><p>Using certified recycled paper from ethical suppliers, we make our packaging 100% recyclable, biodegradable, and plastic-free. In accordance with our FSC certification and commitment to sustainability, 80 percent of our packaging is made from recycled paper, while all of our virgin materials are renewable. <\/p><p>Rather than inserting promotional fliers or inserts, we provide QR codes on our packaging, making it compact and minimal. <\/p>",
            "enlarge_text": false
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "1651266332e6feb2da-0",
        "1651266332e6feb2da-1"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "height": "medium",
        "text_alignment": "center",
        "full_width": false,
        "use_alt_bg": false
      }
    },
    "16512664212c8c8d6b": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "1651266421c49cb4b9-0": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Phasing Out Plastic Waste",
            "use_h1": false
          }
        },
        "1651266421c49cb4b9-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>By eliminating plastic from our packaging, EcoBlvd will have reduced the production of over 3,000 tons of plastic annually, or the equivalent of over 100,00 plastic bottles stacked in a row, covering more than 4,000 miles!<\/p><p>By using smaller packaging, we reduce CO2 emissions from transportation and materials by 5,000 tons each year, which is equivalent to planting 275,000 trees.*<\/p>",
            "enlarge_text": false
          }
        },
        "ca8e66e2-9d01-4126-af9a-27538559c2ea": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><em>*According to internal research and analysis via EPA and Statista.<\/em><\/p>",
            "enlarge_text": false
          }
        }
      },
